  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore <strong>Pocket Cars</strong>, the thrilling <strong>arcade combat-racing</strong> game! Race <strong>RC cars</strong> through dynamic tracks, tackling real-life obstacles with precision. With realistic vehicles featuring impressive off-road capabilities and high-speed boost, get ready for an exhilarating racing experience unlike any other.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170720/extras/662afb1302111a47ec01c8683edeac63.webp?t=1769685423\" width=600 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170720/extras/6219812d003c02e26020c2ebefadfd09.poster.avif?t=1769685423\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170720/extras/6219812d003c02e26020c2ebefadfd09.webm?t=1769685423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170720/extras/6219812d003c02e26020c2ebefadfd09.mp4?t=1769685423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gear up, rev your engines, and get ready to dominate the track in RC Racing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >180+ singleplayer <strong>challenges</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4-player <strong>split-screen</strong> multiplayer.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15-player <strong>online</strong> multiplayer.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170720/extras/f018d513eaa7abf33485ce7ac0af4193.webp?t=1769685423\" width=600 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170720/extras/f0bf33c60cd9c7423c04249e3131b27a.poster.avif?t=1769685423\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170720/extras/f0bf33c60cd9c7423c04249e3131b27a.webm?t=1769685423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170720/extras/f0bf33c60cd9c7423c04249e3131b27a.mp4?t=1769685423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from an arsenal of deadly weapons to outmaneuver and outgun your opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16 <strong>physics-simulated</strong> cars.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16 unique <strong>weapons</strong> including Rocket, Mine, EMP, and more.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170720/extras/273c72fe8a113282032877b1e6b845f3.webp?t=1769685423\" width=600 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170720/extras/7d72fe4eae237d0bb855455e3f1c87f6.poster.avif?t=1769685423\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170720/extras/7d72fe4eae237d0bb855455e3f1c87f6.webm?t=1769685423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170720/extras/7d72fe4eae237d0bb855455e3f1c87f6.mp4?t=1769685423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adventure in the Stunt Arena, where every jump, flip, and crash earns you points!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gravity-defying <strong>stunts</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seamless gameplay with <strong>controller support</strong>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170720/extras/64cd21724b28aecb66468779603840b0.webp?t=1769685423\" width=600 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170720/extras/272371fc87582e2da13e5e05065309e2.poster.avif?t=1769685423\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170720/extras/272371fc87582e2da13e5e05065309e2.webm?t=1769685423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170720/extras/272371fc87582e2da13e5e05065309e2.mp4?t=1769685423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your creativity and personalize your RC car to reflect your unique style!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable <strong>paints, materials, decals</strong>, and gadgets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select wisely <strong>your tires</strong> for enhanced performance.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Don’t forget to wishlist and follow!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170720/extras/bad221ccae439edd4accffe220b7a6c4.poster.avif?t=1769685423\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170720/extras/bad221ccae439edd4accffe220b7a6c4.webm?t=1769685423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170720/extras/bad221ccae439edd4accffe220b7a6c4.mp4?t=1769685423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
